{"word":"ἐγγύς","slug":"ἐγγύς","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἐγγύς</el></b> [<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ etym.\">etym.</a> uncertain] <b>near, close (to)<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> spatially <b><a href='B:480 6:36'>Mk 6:36</a></b> (<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ superl.\">superl.</a>); <b><a href='B:490 19:11'>Lk 19:11</a>; <a href='B:500 3:23'>J 3:23</a></b> and <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ oft.\">oft.</a> in J of geographical localities; <b><a href='B:510 1:12'>Ac 1:12</a>.</b> In imagery <b><a href='B:520 10:8'>Ro 10:8</a>; <a href='B:560 2:13'>Eph 2:13</a>, <a href='B:560 2:17'>17</a></b> (<el>οἱ <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἐγγύς\">ἐγγύς</a></el>); <b><a href='B:650 6:8'>Hb 6:8</a>; <a href='B:650 8:13'>8:13</a>;</b> with component of temporality <b><a href='B:470 24:33'>Mt 24:33</a>; <a href='B:480 13:29'>Mk 13:29</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> temporally <b><a href='B:470 24:32'>Mt 24:32</a>; <a href='B:470 26:18'>26:18</a>; <a href='B:490 21:31'>Lk 21:31</a>; <a href='B:500 6:4'>J 6:4</a>; <a href='B:520 13:11'>Ro 13:11</a></b> (<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ comp.\">comp.</a>); <b><a href='B:570 4:5'>Phil 4:5</a>; <a href='B:730 1:3'>Rv 1:3</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἔγγυος\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἐγγύτερον\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}